        <div class="ps rv"><div class="ps-num-wrap"><span class="ps-n">01</span></div><div class="ps-body"><h3 class="ps-h">Discovery & Strategy</h3><p class="ps-p">Deep immersion in your domain. We map goals, users, and technical constraints before touching a keyboard — because clarity always compounds into velocity.</p></div></div>
        <div class="ps rv d1"><div class="ps-num-wrap"><span class="ps-n">02</span></div><div class="ps-body"><h3 class="ps-h">Architecture & Design</h3><p class="ps-p">System design, API contracts, and a full design system signed off before a single sprint kicks off. No expensive rewrites. No surprises.</p></div></div>
        <div class="ps rv d2"><div class="ps-num-wrap"><span class="ps-n">03</span></div><div class="ps-body"><h3 class="ps-h">Agile Engineering</h3><p class="ps-p">Two-week sprints. Daily standups. Weekly demos. You hold a meaningful opinion on every major decision throughout the build.</p></div></div>
